snippet.textDisplay: People spend a lifetime searching for God. HE dwells in spirited singers like Farida Khanum Ji. One just cannot fathom the depth of her voice and the true notes which come from her even at this age (82 Years). Many other established famous singers who have rendered this song don't even stand a chance to get compared to these heavenly heights. For a singer and musician like me, just to meet a great personality like her and falling at her feet getting her blessings is like being with the Almighty Himself. Stay blessed and live a very long life Farida Ji. Love You ~!
